<br>
Ok, i play a level 7 DE mage on test server.  What i've noticed is not only do i not have all my level 1 or level 4 spells, but with level 8 rapidly approaching (and it seems a lot of good spells at that level) i can't even afford one spell at this point, at about 5pp a pop.<br>
<br>
I've been looting everything i kill, even if it just sells for 8sp.  i've bought no armor or anything either, all i am wearing is my newbie robe, and a cloth belt i looted.<br>
<br>
So, i really have two questions.  <br>
<br>
First, at what level do you finally end up making enough money to cover your spells?<br>
<br>
Second, does anyone have any good tips for making money in the nek area?  Just seems like nothing drops that is worth any decent cash, at least not in my level range.<br>
<br>
Thanks for any replies <br>
<br>
